title: S3 EP5: An American Atelier feat. Peter Do
itunes:title: An American Atelier feat. Peter Do
description: Peter Do is greater than the sum of its parts. While his name is on the door, Peter makes clear that this is not a one man show. This is a company built on friendship and craftsmanship. I sit with the founders of Peter Do, LLC at their Brooklyn Studio.
